  m_text: "PLAYER:\n\n\tWASD / LStick - Move\n\n\tE / A - Interact\n\n\tTAB / X -
    Toggle Inventory\n\n\tESC / START - Pause\n\nOBJECT MOVEMENT:\n\n\tSPACE / RTrigger
    - Pick Up / Put Down Object\n\n\tQ / LTrigger - Orbit Object\n\n\tArrow Keys
    / D-Pad - Rotate Object\n\nINVENTORY:\n\n\tWASD / LStick - Change Slot\n\n\tLeft/Right
